name: Island Boy
description: An Ai Assisted animation using Ebsynth software, based on a TikTok trend video uploaded by @shampanov.pavel. Depicting the likeness of 'Kodiyakredd' mouthing the words to song - Ni Mo Zou ( Kau Jangan Pergi ) 'You Don't Go'. This Ai animation was assisted by 12 individual drawings (frames) and matched to the original video by @shampanov.pavel. Background, Thanos' Farm.
